      <h4><b> Our Mission </b></h4>
      <h6> We aim to achieve the following goals: </h6>
      <ul class="info-list">
        <li> to share students' study experiences for each courses in Purdue. </li>
        <li> to provide students with precise information about the courses. </li>
        <li> to give students the study aids for different courses. </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>




  <div class="footer">
    <a class="about" href="/about"><b>About us</b></a>
